07caf172ba","tid":2290617,"uid":20933,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"今年最佳公廁金獎：荃灣多層停車場公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w274/public/column_images/1118t2.jpg?itok=21bwEzgV\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw274%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F1118t2.jpg%3Fitok%3D21bwEzgV&h=4c3d80d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pof.org.hk/nobarrier/img/items_photo/163886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpof.org.hk%2Fnobarrier%2Fimg%2Fitems_photo%2F163886.jpg&h=9ae0ed3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奪得金獎的荃灣多層停車場公廁除了引入本港新研發的空氣淨化機，又於洗手盤設自動洗手、梘液及乾手功能三合一的設備，改善滴濕地面的問題；而且公廁翻新後採用色彩鮮艷的設計，亦以不同顏色劃分男女廁，徐靖世讚顏色「醒目」之餘亦令使用者「好開心」。此外，公廁鄰近荃灣港鐵站，人流較多但仍能保持衛生，徐靖世認為清潔員工亦值得嘉許。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣多層停車場公廁於2006年曾被協會列為最急待改善公廁之一，徐靖世認為多年來所作的改善，反映負責管理的食環署「擺咗好多心機」，擺脫惡劣情況，稱公廁「由設備到管理都值得嘉許」，應為其開設「最佳進步獎」。"},{"pid":"0f34aff24be64bc7e0c95cded8334c8628580867","tid":2290617,"uid":92700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"整完咪又俾班死廢老整臭曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23763ef1fd99f432cb6beded0f873b89d7ffad6b","tid":2290617,"uid":71433,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2aa73c10ae8cf175ccc68f01fb8ae408b4b6dd02","tid":2290617,"uid":234232,"like":202,"dislike":0,"score":202,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"原來廁所都有協會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"會長你扮咩嘢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d6727bb106ab34e20f3c534f66c2171d5226e6","tid":2290617,"uid":339053,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy"